    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The main issue is that the default line spacing used by `\\n` is wrong for most of our mods.  We avoid this everywhere else by using separate LabelWidgets for each line, which then lets each mod set the spacing that they want.  This is what I was referring to when I was talking about two line tooltips.\n\nHow about creating a dynamic `MULTI_LINE_TOOLTIP` that creates as many label widgets as required (with margins inherited from the y offset of the label - check some of the other tooltips)?  This isn't a huge change from what you have here and gives us the extra flexibility.\n"
  },
